citations.desc: ACCESS AND INSPECTION OF RECORDS AND PROPERTY; SUBMISSION OF ITINERARIES.
citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 2:50 pm on
15-Apr-19.
The inspector arrived at the facility at approximately 2:50 pm and spoke to a household member who stated that no
one was available for the inspection. The inspector called the licensee's phone number, but was unable to leave a
message.
